  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/594b2d12bda8e9f05d8a0e37d0d71566.poster.avif?t=1745903664\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/594b2d12bda8e9f05d8a0e37d0d71566.webm?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/594b2d12bda8e9f05d8a0e37d0d71566.mp4?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Bing and Bong between the top and bottom of the screen, dodging obstacles, collecting points, and smashing power-ups. Survive as long as possible in this fast-paced minimalist arcade experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/634d535499653e3d5322cee8e6a607a1.poster.avif?t=1745903664\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/634d535499653e3d5322cee8e6a607a1.webm?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/634d535499653e3d5322cee8e6a607a1.mp4?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Simple one-button gameplay, tap to brake and control your movement. Play with a <strong>Controller, Keyboard, or Mouse</strong> for seamless input.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/e3882b7a9f05f8f03f080023863e5dbc.poster.avif?t=1745903664\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/e3882b7a9f05f8f03f080023863e5dbc.webm?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/e3882b7a9f05f8f03f080023863e5dbc.mp4?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Easy to pick up, hard to master</strong> – Simple controls with deep challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Score-Chasing Action</strong> – The game speeds up and gets harder over time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Skins</strong> – Featuring characters from other Adamvision Studios games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>‘Close Call’ System</strong> – Earn extra points for near misses with obstacles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards & Steam Achievements</strong> – Compete globally for the highest score</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Cloud Support</strong> – Keep progress synced across devices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Trading Cards</strong> – Includes profile wallpapers & emoticons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Perfect for quick sessions</strong> – Play a round while waiting in queue for another game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quirky Sound Design</strong> – Audio SFX created using my own voice + royalty-free sounds</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/50708eef5b94a8f697a3c63bd3a22328.poster.avif?t=1745903664\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/50708eef5b94a8f697a3c63bd3a22328.webm?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/50708eef5b94a8f697a3c63bd3a22328.mp4?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Bing Bong XL is a <strong>small, replayable arcade score-chaser</strong> designed for quick, high-intensity gameplay. As the first in my minimalist arcade series, it builds upon my original mobile game ‘Bing Bong’ with refined mechanics and features suited for PC.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I love making simple arcade games and truly appreciate feedback. If you find a bug, have suggestions, or just want to say hello, reach out via <strong>Discord</strong> or my <strong>Website</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks for playing!<br><strong>Adam Nickerson - Adamvision Studios</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><br><br><br><strong>Song:</strong><br>I Wanna Live by Novalight<br>SoundCloud – Licensed under Creative Commons CC BY 3.0</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/594b2d12bda8e9f05d8a0e37d0d71566.poster.avif?t=1745903664\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/594b2d12bda8e9f05d8a0e37d0d71566.webm?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/594b2d12bda8e9f05d8a0e37d0d71566.mp4?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Bing and Bong between the top and bottom of the screen, dodging obstacles, collecting points, and smashing power-ups. Survive as long as possible in this fast-paced minimalist arcade experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/634d535499653e3d5322cee8e6a607a1.poster.avif?t=1745903664\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/634d535499653e3d5322cee8e6a607a1.webm?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/634d535499653e3d5322cee8e6a607a1.mp4?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Simple one-button gameplay, tap to brake and control your movement. Play with a <strong>Controller, Keyboard, or Mouse</strong> for seamless input.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/e3882b7a9f05f8f03f080023863e5dbc.poster.avif?t=1745903664\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/e3882b7a9f05f8f03f080023863e5dbc.webm?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/e3882b7a9f05f8f03f080023863e5dbc.mp4?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Easy to pick up, hard to master</strong> – Simple controls with deep challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Score-Chasing Action</strong> – The game speeds up and gets harder over time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Skins</strong> – Featuring characters from other Adamvision Studios games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>‘Close Call’ System</strong> – Earn extra points for near misses with obstacles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards & Steam Achievements</strong> – Compete globally for the highest score</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Cloud Support</strong> – Keep progress synced across devices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Trading Cards</strong> – Includes profile wallpapers & emoticons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Perfect for quick sessions</strong> – Play a round while waiting in queue for another game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quirky Sound Design</strong> – Audio SFX created using my own voice + royalty-free sounds</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/50708eef5b94a8f697a3c63bd3a22328.poster.avif?t=1745903664\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/50708eef5b94a8f697a3c63bd3a22328.webm?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840930/extras/50708eef5b94a8f697a3c63bd3a22328.mp4?t=1745903664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Bing Bong XL is a <strong>small, replayable arcade score-chaser</strong> designed for quick, high-intensity gameplay. As the first in my minimalist arcade series, it builds upon my original mobile game ‘Bing Bong’ with refined mechanics and features suited for PC.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I love making simple arcade games and truly appreciate feedback. If you find a bug, have suggestions, or just want to say hello, reach out via <strong>Discord</strong> or my <strong>Website</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks for playing!<br><strong>Adam Nickerson - Adamvision Studios</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><br><br><br><strong>Song:</strong><br>I Wanna Live by Novalight<br>SoundCloud – Licensed under Creative Commons CC BY 3.0</p>",
